name.value: MDS Logical Model to FHIR Mapping

description.value: Maps elements from the MDSRoadSafety logical model to target FHIR R4 resources.

name.value: Road Safety AllergyIntolerance

description.value: Known allergies, substances and reactions.

name.value: Road Safety Claim

description.value: Claim information related to cost of care.

name.value: Road Safety Condition

description.value: Conditions used for medical history, initial impression, ICD-10 nature/external cause, and final diagnosis entries.

name.value: Road Safety DocumentReference (Evidence)

description.value: Evidence and post-crash documentation linked to the incident (e.g., cause of crash, party at fault, incident management logs, CCTV, shape files).

name.value: Road Safety Encounter

description.value: Encounter for EMS run report / facility submission context. Captures incident number, type, timing, participants, disposition & transfer.

name.value: Road Safety Incident Location

description.value: Location of incident; supports PH-Core address extensions and geolocation.

name.value: Road Safety MedicationStatement

description.value: Current medications as codeable concepts or references where available.

name.value: Road Safety Minimum Dataset (MDS) Logical Model

description.value: Abstract, sectioned logical model for the PH Road Safety MDS covering incident, patient, encounter, clinical, vitals, injuries, evidence/documents, workflow, and finance. Elements mirror the CSV rows; mappings point to target FHIR elements for subsequent profiling.

name.value: Road Safety Observation

description.value: Generic base Observation for road safety data; specialized concept profiles below constrain code/value patterns.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Abrasion

description.value: Abrasion present; with optional site and details.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Activity at Time of Incident

description.value: Activity of the patient at time of incident; allow text fallback.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Avulsion

description.value: Avulsion present; with optional site and details.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Blood Pressure

description.value: Blood pressure using component entries for systolic/diastolic.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Body Temperature

description.value: Body temperature.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Burn 1st Degree

description.value: 1st degree burn present; with site and details.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Burn 2nd Degree

description.value: 2nd degree burn present; with site and details.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Burn 3rd Degree

description.value: 3rd degree burn present; with site and details.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Burn 4th Degree

description.value: 4th degree burn present; with site and details.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Call Source

description.value: Call source description (free text).

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Collision Type

description.value: Collision type (Angle, Head-on, Rear end, Side swipe, etc.).

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Collision vs Non-Collision

description.value: Indicates whether the incident was collision or non-collision.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Concussion

description.value: Concussion present; with site and details.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Contusion

description.value: Contusion present; with site and details.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Cyanosis

description.value: Cyanosis assessment.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Date/Time of Injury

description.value: Timestamp of injury occurrence.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Date/Time Received by EMS

description.value: Calendar/timestamp the EMS/dispatch received the request.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - External Cause: Bites/Stings

description.value: Flag indicating bites/stings.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - External Cause: Bites/Stings Agent

description.value: Specific animal/insect/plant agent.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - External Cause: Burns

description.value: Flag indicating burns as external cause.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - External Cause: Burns (Other specify)

description.value: Other text for burn cause.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - External Cause: Burns Agent

description.value: Agent causing burn (heat/electric/chemical/etc.).

name.value: Road Safety Observation - External Cause: Chemical (Specify)

description.value: Specific chemical/substance.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - External Cause: Chemical/Substance

description.value: Flag indicating chemical/substance exposure.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - External Cause: Contact with Sharp Object

description.value: Flag indicating sharp object cause.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - External Cause: Drowning

description.value: Flag indicating drowning.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - External Cause: Drowning (Other specify)

description.value: Other text for water type.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - External Cause: Drowning Type/Body of Water

description.value: Type/body of water.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - External Cause: Exposure to Forces of Nature

description.value: Flag indicating exposure to natural disaster/calamity.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - External Cause: Fall

description.value: Flag indicating fall.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - External Cause: Fall (Specifics)

description.value: Where/what patient fell from (stairs, ladder, etc.).

name.value: Road Safety Observation - External Cause: Firecracker

description.value: Flag indicating firecracker-related cause.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - External Cause: Firecracker (Type)

description.value: Type of firecracker (text).

name.value: Road Safety Observation - External Cause: Gunshot

description.value: Flag indicating gunshot.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - External Cause: Gunshot (Weapon)

description.value: Weapon type (text).

name.value: Road Safety Observation - External Cause: Hanging/Strangulation

description.value: Flag indicating hanging/strangulation.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - External Cause: Mauling/Assault

description.value: Flag indicating assault.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - External Cause: Other

description.value: Flag indicating other external cause.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - External Cause: Other (Specify)

description.value: Other cause (text).

name.value: Road Safety Observation - External Cause: Sexual Assault/Abuse/Rape (Alleged)

description.value: Flag indicating sexual assault.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - External Cause: Sharp Object (Specify)

description.value: Specify object (free text).

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Fracture (Closed)

description.value: Closed fracture present; with site and details.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Fracture (Open)

description.value: Open fracture present; with site and details.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Glasgow Coma Scale

description.value: GCS with components for eyes, verbal, motor; optional total score as integer.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - How Many Patients Involved

description.value: Count of patients involved.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - How Many Vehicles Involved

description.value: Count of vehicles involved.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Injury Intent

description.value: Intent of injury (Unintentional, Intentional-self, Intentional-violence, Undetermined).

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Level of Consciousness (AVPU)

description.value: Level of consciousness (e.g., AVPU).

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Mode of Transport to Facility

description.value: Mode of transport to the hospital/facility; allow coded value with optional text for 'Others'.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Multiple Injuries?

description.value: Boolean flag indicating multiple injuries.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Open Wound

description.value: Open wound present; with site and details.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Other Risk Factors

description.value: Other risk factors at the time of incident; allow text for 'Others'.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Other Specified Injury

description.value: Other specified injury present; with site and details.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Other Vehicle/Object Involved

description.value: Other vehicle/object type involved; text for 'Others'.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Patient's Vehicle

description.value: Type of vehicle used by patient; text for 'Others'.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Place of Occurrence

description.value: Place type where injury occurred; name can be carried in note when applicable.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Position of Patient

description.value: Seat/position (driver/front passenger/rear/pedestrian); text for 'Others'.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Presence of Traffic Investigator

description.value: Boolean presence/absence of traffic investigator.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Priority Level (Urgency)

description.value: System-generated urgency level per CAD/agency rules.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Pulse Rate

description.value: Pulse/heart rate in beats/min.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Pupils

description.value: Pupil size/reactivity summary.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Reported Complaint

description.value: Free-text reported complaint.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Respiratory Rate

description.value: Respiratory rate in breaths/min.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Safety Accessories

description.value: Safety accessories present/used; allow text for 'Others'.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Time Departed Scene

description.value: Timestamp unit departed scene.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Time Enroute

description.value: Timestamp when unit dispatched/began traveling.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Time of Emergency Station Arrival

description.value: Timestamp unit returned to base/became available.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Time of Hospital Arrival

description.value: Timestamp unit arrived at receiving facility.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Time On Scene

description.value: Timestamp crew arrived at scene.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Transport/Vehicular Accident (flag)

description.value: Boolean flag indicating transport/vehicular accident.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Traumatic Amputation

description.value: Traumatic amputation present; with site and details.

name.value: Road Safety Observation - Triage Priority

description.value: Triage category assigned at scene (e.g., Red/Yellow/Green/Black).

name.value: Road Safety Patient

description.value: Patient demographics and identifiers for road safety reporting; reuse PH-Core address extensions for barangay/city/province/region.

name.value: Road Safety Procedure

description.value: Procedures related to incident/report (e.g., coordination with receiving hospital, psychosocial support, interventions).

name.value: Road Safety ServiceRequest

description.value: Requests or records related to refusal to admit and related workflow signals.
